name: CIBC Global Bond ex-Canada Index ETF (CAD-Hedged)
longDescription: The ETF Seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of a global aggregate bond index that measures the investment return of the global investment grade bond market, excluding Canada. Currently, this CIBC ETF seeks to track the Morningstar Global exCanada Core Bond Hedged CAD Index (or any successor thereto).
